Description: Methods for converting elemental counts acquired by XRF scanners to reference elemental concentrations acquired by conventional methods such as ICP (Kabiri et al. (2022) <doi>, Weltje and Tjalingii (2008) <doi:10.1016/j.epsl.2008.07.054>).
